<h1>Return Policy</h1>

<h2>Returns and Exchanges</h2>

<p>At My Shop, we want you to be completely satisfied with your purchase. If you are not satisfied for any reason, you may return eligible items within [Number] days of the delivery date for a refund or exchange.</p>

<h3>Eligibility for Returns</h3>
<p>To be eligible for a return, your item must be:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Unused, unworn, and in the same condition that you received it.</li>
  <li>In its original packaging with all tags attached.</li>
  <li>Accompanied by the original receipt or proof of purchase.</li>
</ul>
<p>Please note that some items, such as [Caps, Hats, etc], may not be eligible for return. This will be clearly stated on the product page.</p>

<h3>How to Initiate a Return or Exchange</h3>
<p>To initiate a return or exchange, please follow these steps:</p>
<ol>
  <li>Contact us at [genshemanipaljaipur@gmail.com] with your order number and reason for return.</li>
  <li>Once your return request is approved, you will receive instructions on how to return your item.</li>
  <li>Carefully package the item(s) you are returning, including the original packing slip or a note with your order number.</li>
  <li>Ship the item(s) to the address provided in the return instructions.</li>
</ol>

<h3>Refunds</h3>
<p>Once we receive your returned item and inspect it, we will send you an email to notify you that we have received your returned item. We will also notify you of the approval or rejection of your refund.</p>
<p>If your return is approved, your refund will be processed, and a credit will automatically be applied to your original method of payment within [7-10] working days.</p>

<h3>Exchanges</h3>
<p>If you wish to exchange an item, please indicate this when you contact us to initiate the return. Exchanges are subject to availability. If the desired item is not available, a refund will be issued.</p>

<h3>Shipping Costs for Returns</h3>
<p>Shipping costs for returning an item are the responsibility of the customer, unless the item is defective or incorrect due to our error.</p>

